import react from "react"
import styled from "styled-components"
import Video from "./Video"
const Videos = () => {

    return (
        <>
            <Main>
                <Video />
                <Video />
                <Video />
                <Video />
            </Main>
            <Main>
                <Video />
                <Video />
                <Video />
                <Video />
            </Main>
        </>
    )
}

export default Videos

const Main = styled.div`
width: 100%;
min-height: 100vh;
display: flex;
`
